    <section><title>Installing CocoBlog</title>
      <section><title>CVS</title>
<p>Login:</p>
<ul>
<li>cvs -d:pserver:anonymous@cvs.cocoblog.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/cocoblog login</li>
<li>password: empty password, just hit return</li>
</ul>

<p>Checkout:</p>
<ul>
<li>cvs -z3 -d:pserver:anonymous@cvs.cocoblog.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/cocoblog co cocoon-cocoblog</li>
</ul>

<p>Update:</p>
<ul>
<li>cvs -z3 -d:pserver:anonymous@cvs.cocoblog.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/cocoblog -q update -d</li>
</ul>
      </section>

      <section><title>Compiling/Building and Installing</title>
<ul>
<li>export JAVA_HOME=/usr/local/jdk1.3.1</li>
<li>export ANT_HOME=/usr/local/jakarta-ant-1.4.1</li>
<li>export PATH=/usr/local/jakarta-ant-1.4.1/bin:$PATH</li>
<li>ant -Dwebapp.dir=/usr/local/jakarta-tomcat-4.0.4-b3/webapps/cocoon</li>
</ul>
      </section>



      <section><title>Fix HSQLDB bug</title>
<ul>
<li>cp ~/src/cocoon-cocobloglib/excalibur-datasource-1.0.jar /usr/local/jakarta-tomcat-4.0.4-b3/webapps/cocoon/WEB-INF/lib/excalibur-datasource-vm12-20020820.jar</li>
</ul>
      </section>


      <section><title>Populate Database</title>
<ul>
<li>
/usr/local/jdk1.3.1/bin/java -cp ~/src/cocoon-cocoblog/lib/hsqldb-1.7.0.jar org.hsqldb.util.DatabaseManagerSwing
</li>
<li>URL = jdbc:hsqldb:hsql://localhost:9002</li>
</ul>
      </section>
    </section>



